      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Benefits and pensions for UK nationals in the EU, EEA or Switzerland if there's a no-deal Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This guidance explains the rights of UK nationals in the EU, European Economic Area (EEA) or Switzerland to benefits and pensions if there’s a no-deal Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

